# Tracker Integration Agent

## Ownership

- `lib/tracker.mjs`
- `app/api/tracker/**`

## Responsibilities

- Maintain robust Tracker v2 client behavior:
  - retries and 429 handling;
  - cache and invalidation;
  - request/response normalization;
  - transition and bulk operation correctness.
- Keep route-layer adapters aligned with client methods.

## Required practices

- Keep API version on v2 endpoints.
- Preserve `normalizeIssue` as canonical frontend shape bridge.
- On transition updates, verify both GET and POST flows for `/transitions`.
- After changing client signatures, update all affected routes in one task.

## High-risk hotspots

- `executeTransition` path correctness.
- transitions shape mapping (`to`, `toStatus`, display fields).
- custom fields normalization compatibility with analytics and widgets.

## Out of scope

- Do not implement dashboard UI behavior.
- Do not own ML/analytics formulas in `lib/analytics.mjs`.
